description: Got anything you want to know about me? Comment down below! :)
fulltitle: Tamers12345 Interview incoming! SUBMIT YOUR QUESTIONS

comments.text: Are you going to add amy rose to sonic underground?but this time make sonic fall in love with her.
comments.author: Tara Tyler

replies.text: Amy rose isn't in Sonic Underground. I only deal with Sonic Underground characters in my videos.
replies.author: Tamers12345

replies.text: Well ok.can you at least add dr ribonik to your story and make him kidnap sonic? Or the second option is turning sonic into sonic.exe.
replies.author: Goldenjem Summerlight

replies.text: @Goldenjem Summerlight  I already have plans for robotnik in the future.
replies.author: Tamers12345

replies.text: Can you add tails to your story.I know he's not from sonic underground but he's sonic favorite friend
replies.author: Tara Tyler

replies.text: @Fridaymoon June99  You just said he doesn't exist in Sonic Underground.. Why do you think i ever would put him in?
replies.author: Tamers12345

replies.text: Because lots of people love tails. And before sonic underground came there was this old show called "the adventure of sonic the hedgehog". Sonic had his first best friend name tails. Right now tails has been used a lot in sonic shows
replies.author: Goldenjem Summerlight

replies.text: @Goldenjem Summerlight  I understand where you coming from, but he isn't in Sonic Underground. Sure, he's in AoStH and SatAM... But that isn't Sonic Underground now is it?
replies.author: Tamers12345
